    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-01-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-01-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="143" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d143">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">White</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-01-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 10, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.
                            (Received January 11.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Russian minister for foreign affairs asks whether the United States is
                        inclined to entertain proposals for modus regarding North Pacific seal
                        fisheries like that now existing between Russia and Great Britain. If so,
                        Russian Government will present such proposal. Dispatch follows.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
